node.text:
our guest bathroom ✨ 
.
complete with a couple diy projects from my bag of tricks. this is the first bathroom I got to use our own “sss quarterline” cabinet fronts from my line with @semihandmade on a vanity, which makes this maybe my most epic ikea hack to date?! 
I also used the wood appliance pulls from my hardware line for @parkstudio_la as drawer pulls for their extra large size. and shall we talk about the gorgeous jumbo @alliedmaker sconce? #sssinteriors #samuelfamilyfixer

node.text:
took a lot of convincing with the result of a lot of side eyes when @gaiahousecafe_gr owner, Andrea, and I explained to any and all contractors that we did not want the ceiling touched. Thought at one point we might have to strap ourselves to the joists 😂.

when she bought the building it had already been gutted down to the studs and stripped of any character, so it was one of the the only chances to save a bit of a patina from the old space. #sssinteriors #thenewgaiahousecafe
